  "title": "Lorry Driver & Installation Technician",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Operate company lorry safely and responsibly in accordance with Singapore traffic regulations (Class 4 Driving License required).</p></li><li><p>Deliver products to customer sites, warehouses, and project locations.</p></li><li><p>Assist with loading and unloading of goods, ensuring proper handling and securing of items.</p></li><li><p>Perform basic on-site installation of products at customer premises (simple mechanical assembly, positioning, and setup).</p></li><li><p>Support technicians or engineers during installation and servicing activities when required. </p></li><li><p>Conduct basic functional checks after installation and report any issues to the supervisor.</p></li><li><p>Maintain delivery records, job sheets, gate passes, and installation checklists.</p></li><li><p>Comply with company safety procedures and customer site regulations at all times.</p></li></ul>",
